summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Parks and Recreation; authorizing the Superintendent of Parks and Recreation to execute an agreement with Interbay Family Golf Centers, Inc., to develop, operate and maintain the Interbay Golf Center; and, authorizing the relocation of the P-Patch consistent with the Agreement between the Department of of Parks and Recreation and the Department of Housing and Human Services.
